item.title: 【Requests】[REQ PIC] - Mariah Carey - Daydream (Alternate Artwork)
item.description:
Can anyone make this alternate artwork to Daydream, as seen for the back cover of the Always Be My Baby Maxi.

It seemingly just keeps it's original background color of the image or just a little more on the whiter side than the original grey in the photoshoot picture.


Official Alternate cover on the maxi: https://www.dangerousdevotion.com/cdn/shop/products/20230418_114111_1024x1024@2x.jpg?v=1681843478


HQ image taken from Fantasy Digital Single of the pic for my request: https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EfZ8IyIX0AEsHIN?format=jpg&name=4096x4096


HQ album cover of Daydream: https://albumartexchange.com/coverart/gallery/ma/mariahcarey_daydream_e43j.jpg


Can anyone possibly make it 1500x1500 or 2000x2000?

Thank you for this!
